---
// Hero section - Name, one-liner, current work
---

<section class="mb-16">
  <!-- Name with accent underline -->
  <div class="mb-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-2 inline-block">
      Hey, I'm Beaux.
      <span class="block h-1 bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2 w-24"></span>
    </h1>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Location with status -->
  <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] text-base mb-8 flex items-center font-mono">
    <span class="status-dot"></span>
    Powell River, BC · Available for projects
  </p>
  
  <!-- Tagline in a subtle card -->
  <div class="card p-6 md:p-8">
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Building the operating system for AI agents.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-muted)]">
      Army mechanic turned self-taught developer. I build open source infrastructure that makes AI agents smarter, cheaper, and more reliable — memory systems, context management, predictive execution, and multi-agent orchestration. One interconnected ecosystem, all MIT-licensed.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
